Version 0.4
===========

* fixed bugs:
  * https://gna.org/bugs/?12022
  * https://gna.org/bugs/?12025
  * https://gna.org/bugs/?12029
  * https://gna.org/bugs/?12029

* added a wrapper function that strips newlines at the beginning and ending of a string
* added a parameter "--bug" for debugging purposes
* "attribute" is not longer whitelisted
* real numbers are only anonymized if not already processing an element that is anonymized anyway (e.g. <description>-Tags)
* the "wbim" namespace is now optional, but code is generated with "wbim:"-prefix


Version 0.3
===========

* fixed bugs:
  * http://gna.org/bugs/?11677
  * http://gna.org/bugs/?11678
  * http://gna.org/bugs/?11679

* "type" and "instanceOf" not longer whitelisted
* real numbers in any element are replaced by 0.0
* the values "true" and "false" are whitelisted to avoid syntax error
